The paper discusses physical-layer security in cognitive radio networks, which involves topics related to cryptography, information theory, networking, and system design. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.MM (Multimedia).
